title: The Next Move: WiSE JP Online Study Session
description:
Have you been working on a side project? Do you want to be self-accountable for your progress and share your knowledge with the community? Are you excited to share insights into a tech topic/ software platform you have been learning?

 This event is a great place to do so.
 We will share the link (Google Meet) on the day of the event.

title: The Next Move: WiSE JP Online Study Session
description:
We are excited to host our next in-person event at Code Chrysalis!

 WiSE JP is focused on empowering diverse women in Japan to succeed in technology careers. This event will focus on how to make technical accomplishments more visible, both inside your company and in the wider tech community. Expect a mix of insights, interactive activities, and peer learning.

  Enjoy delicious food and drinks while networking with like-minded professionals. Connect with other women and allies who share your passion for technology.
address: 106-0046, Minato City, Motoazabu, 3-chōme−1−３５ Vort元麻布 B2F
